name: Skyscrapers of the andes
description: I am from Bogotá Colombia, which as a strange thing in Hollywood movies has been shown as a small town with 3 houses with a court and a church in the middle of a hill, indeed we have buildings that tickle the clouds and the stars not only they are tall because they are tall buildings, but Bogota is located more than two thousand meters above sea level, it is old, it is modern, it is made of brick, it has natural wonders, it is chaos, you survive from it and you live in her, if these Hyperlapses are useful for something, it is to show her beyond her rudeness, hopefully so.
